# Parser sibling

- Author parser-engine changes in `../cedocumentmapper_v2.0`, add a fixture and
  regression test there, then re-vendor the pinned source.
- Do not rederive parsing rules in the web app, Data API, or orchestration.
- Keep the deterministic rule engine as the deployed default.
- Run the vendor-pin verifier after every re-vendor.
- Internal classification fields must never enter the twelve-field EVA export.
